Titolo: The Elder Scrolls: Legends

Anno: 2017

Descrizione: The Elder Scrolls: Legends is a free-to-play digital collectible card video game, published by Bethesda Softworks for Microsoft Windows, iOS, macOS and Android in 2017.
Bethesda announced in December 2019 that development on Legends had been halted, though the game and servers remain available for play.